Poetry - Package Information

Use the [prgm]poetry show[/prgm] command to view information about installed packages.

# Viewing installed packages
$ [prgm]poetry show[/prgm]                        # List all installed packages
$ [prgm]poetry show[/prgm] [arg]--tree[/arg]                 # Show dependency tree

# Viewing out-of-date packages
$ [prgm]poetry show[/prgm] [arg]--outdated[/arg]             # Show only outdated packages
$ [prgm]poetry show[/prgm] [arg]--latest[/arg]               # Show latest available versions
